Package ch.iserver.ace.collaboration.jupiter

Interface Summary
AcknowledgeAction An AcknowledgeAction is passed to an AcknowledgeStrategy to define what should happen if the AcknowledgeStrategy determines it is time to send an acknowledge.
AcknowledgeStrategy An AcknowledgeStrategy determines how and when an AcknowledgeAction should be executed.
AcknowledgeStrategyFactory An AcknowledgeStrategyFactory creates AcknowledgeStrategy objects.
AlgorithmWrapper Wrapper interface for algorithm instances.
ConfigurableSession ConfigurableSession objects are returned from the session factory.
DocumentRegistry A registry and factory for MutableRemoteDocument objects.
MutableRemoteDocument Mutable variant of the RemoteDocument interface.
MutableRemoteUser Mutable variant of the RemoteUser interface.
PublisherConnection A ParticipantConnection to the publisher of the document.
SessionConnectionWrapper.FailureHandler FailureHandler for SessionConnectionWrapper objects.
SessionFactory Factory object for participant sessions.
UserRegistry Registry class and factory for RemoteUser objects.

CountingAcknowledgeStrategy A simple acknowledge strategy that counts incoming messages.
CountingAcknowledgeStrategyFactory Factory that creates CountingAcknowledgeStrategy objects.
JoinRequestImpl The default implementation of the JoinRequest interface.
NullAcknowledgeStrategy AcknowledgeStrategy that does not schedule any acknowledge messages.
NullAcknowledgeStrategyFactory AcknowledgeStrategyFactory that creates NullAcknowledgeStrategy instances.

PublishedSessionImpl Default implementation of the PublishedSession interface.

SessionImpl Default implementation of the Session interface.
UserRegistryImpl The default implementation of a UserRegistry.
